  <brief_title>Efficacy of Narrative Exposure Therapy (NET) in Treating Women After Human Trafficking or Forced Prostitution</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effectiveness of Narrative Exposure Therapy in Treating Women After Trafficking and Forced Prostitution</official_title>
